            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[LEGO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[The Nightmare Before Christmas]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[圣诞夜惊魂]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1256927</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不时推出经典电影主题积木套装的 LEGO，日前宣布为导演添布顿的 1993 年经典奇幻定格动画电影作品《圣诞夜惊魂》（The Nightmare Before Christmas），推出同名积木套装。积木将电影的三个经典场景重现，分别为旋转山、杰克骷髅王的家和万圣镇市政厅。</p><p><span id="more-1256927"></span></p><p>LEGO 将《圣诞夜惊魂》中的经典细节，例如会走路的浴缸、杰克的圣诞配方黑板、市政厅的讲台等等呈现，电影的粉丝们相信会感到满意。此外，套装还包含 8 个 Minifigs 迷你人偶，包括电影中的主要角色杰克骷髅王、莎莉、圣诞老人、Lock、Shock、Barrel、Zero the Dog，以及一个双面表情造型的市长。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/nasa-bp-agreement/fun-tech/attachment/08182b/" rel="attachment wp-att-1256941"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1256941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08182b-694x340.jpg" alt="《圣诞夜惊魂》LEGO" width="694" height="340" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08182b-694x340.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/08182b.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>这套《圣诞夜惊魂》LEGO 套装由 2,193 块积木组成，目标顾客是成年而非儿童，完成后的尺寸约为 48.2 x 27.8 x 31.2cm。玩家可以利用 LEGO Builder 应用程式，以 3D 观看工具欣赏这套装和相关影片。套装编号为 21351，售价为 199.99 美元（约 1,559 港元），9 月 6 日正式上市。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_52125"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/A1-pOZjIIqQ?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.newelementary.com/2024/08/21351-nightmare-before-christmas.html">newelementary</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/lego-zh1/dc/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LEGO ZH1 菲林相机即将实现，最后还差 850 个支持者</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/05/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%b8%ad%e5%ad%b8%e7%94%9f%e7%8e%a9-first-lego-league-%e5%8f%83%e5%8a%a0%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e8%b3%bd/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">香港学生玩 FIRST LEGO League 参加世界赛</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/lego%e3%80%81%e4%bb%bb%e5%a4%a9%e5%a0%82%e5%86%8d%e5%ba%a6%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c-%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e3%80%8a%e8%96%a9%e7%88%be%e9%81%94%e5%82%b3%e8%aa%aa%e3%80%8b%e7%a9%8d%e6%9c%a8%e5%a5%97%e8%a3%9d/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">LEGO、任天堂再度合作，推出《萨尔达传说》积木套装</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/18/lego-21351-nightmare-before-christmas/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/">添布顿经典《圣诞夜惊魂》   LEGO 套装还原三大电影场景</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
